dialogStrings:
“Hey you!!
What're you lookin' so down for!?”

“How 'bout it?
Want me to read your fortune!?
A bright future! A happy future!”{PAUSE}“Oh, but don't hold it against me
if it doesn't come true!”

“Oh, so sorry!
I'm a fortune telling machine.
The name's…”

{Cait Sith}
“You kidding?
I can find missing things,
missing people, anything!”

{Cloud}
“Then can you tell me where
a man named Sephiroth is?”

{Cloud}
“…Ordinary luck.
It will be an active fortune.”{PAUSE}“Give into the good will of others, and
something big'll happen after summer.
…Wait…hold on…”

{Cloud}
“Be careful of forgetfulness.
Your lucky color is…blue?”

{Cait Sith}
“Wait, wait give me another chance!”{PAUSE}“Wait! Let me try it again!”

{Cloud}
“What you pursue will be yours.
But you will lose something dear.”

{Cait Sith}
“I don't know if it's good
or bad…”{PAUSE}“This's the first time I
ever got something like THIS.”

{Cait Sith}
“Being a fortune teller,
this is gonna bug me.{PAUSE}“If I don't see how it turns out,
I'll never be able to relax.
So, I'm going with you!”

{Red XIII}
“{Cloud}, it's all right with you?”

{Cait Sith}
“I'm comin' with you no matter WHAT you say!”

“Let's get lotsa GP at Wonder Square
and have some fun!”

“Let's get lotsa GP at Wonder Square
and have a blast!”

“I'll hang in there,
even if I'm alone!”

“They probably told you
at the entrance, but
most of the attractions at
Gold Saucer only take 'GP'.”{PAUSE}“They don't sell GP.
You can only get 'em from the
Wonder Square games or at the
Chocobo Races.”

{Aeris}
“There's no time for that!!
Let's hurry and go after {Cait Sith}!”

{Tifa}
“There's no time to relax.
Let's hurry and go after {Cait Sith}!”

{Yuffie}
“Is there time to be fooling around?
Weren't we goin' after {Cait Sith}?”

{Barret}
“What the hell are you doing!?
We gotta get that damn cat!”
